      Founding Hosts don't need to spend much time upfront creating content. All you need to do is decide on a time and topic with one or two colleagues, think of a few talking points, and encourage fans & donors to join in. <br><br>

      <%= link_to 'Try it out! ', "/signup" %> Message info@CrowdPublish.TV if you know someone who should become a potential Founding Host.<br><br>

